text: Pfarrkirchen is a municipality in southern Lower Bavaria Germany, the capital of the district Rottal-Inn. It may also refer to: *Pfarrkirchen bei Bad Hall, a municipality in the district of Steyr-Land in the Austrian state of Upper Austria *Pfarrkirchen im Mühlkreis, municipality in the district of Rohrbach in the Austrian state of Upper Austria
title: Pfarrkirchen (disambiguation)
